( Reuters : China Daily ) Child rescuedAmid the rescue efforts , a 30 - year - old pregnant woman surnamed Zhao was pulled out of the rubble along with a young child and sent to hospital for treatment , the People ' s Daily said on its Weibo account . A local TV journalist due to get married on Saturday instead turned up for work and a photograph of her holding a microphone in her wedding dress with bright make - up and a corsage was widely circulated online . A two - year - old girl with heavy bandages wrapped around her bloodstained head was brought in as AFP watched doctors attend to her ." Please .